{
  "frontCover": "Front cover of a greeting card with a 9:16 aspect ratio, rendered in a soft watercolor painting style. The scene features two charming, simplified cartoon-style characters: a young man on the left with short dark hair and a grey t-shirt, and a young woman on the right with long dark hair, glasses, and a light blue dress. They are positioned to the left and center of the frame. In the upper right portion of the card, a vibrant, swirling nebula of deep purples, blues, and hints of pink and orange is depicted, speckled with numerous small white and golden stars. The word \"Love\" is elegantly scripted in a flowing white font, positioned centrally within the nebula. A large paintbrush, held by the young man, is shown with its bristles dipping into the colorful nebula, as if painting it, with streaks of purple and pink paint appearing to trail from the brush onto the card's lighter, textured background. The overall mood is warm, sincere, and artistic, with visible watercolor brush strokes and organic paint bleeds creating a soft, blended effect. The text \"Love\" is safely placed within the central area, avoiding the top and bottom 10% edges.",
  "backCover": "Back cover of a greeting card with a 9:16 aspect ratio, rendered in a soft watercolor painting style, complementing the front cover. The design features subtle, organic watercolor washes in soft blues, purples, and pinks, reminiscent of the nebula on the front but more diffused and ethereal. Scattered across the background are a few delicate, stylized golden stars and subtle paint splatters, suggesting a continuation of the celestial theme. The composition is minimalist and serene, with no text or characters. The artwork utilizes soft brush strokes and organic paint bleeds, creating a peaceful and artistic closure to the visual narrative. The colors are muted and flowing, providing a gentle, complementary ending.",
  "leftInterior": "Left interior page of a greeting card with a 9:16 aspect ratio, created in a soft watercolor painting style. This page depicts a continuation of the artistic narrative, showcasing a vast, dreamlike expanse of watercolor clouds and subtle celestial elements. Soft washes of pastel blues, purples, and hints of pink blend organically, creating an ethereal and expansive atmosphere. Floating within this celestial dreamscape are abstract, whimsical shapes and faint stardust effects, suggesting a journey through a personal universe. Subtle, flowing brush strokes and gentle color transitions are prominent, maintaining the artistic style and tone of the front cover. The focus is on creating a visually rich, imaginative, and emotional backdrop, hinting at the boundless nature of love without literal representation. The composition is artistic and evocative, designed to evoke a sense of wonder and deep emotion, with no text or characters present.",
  "rightInterior": "Right interior page of a greeting card with a 9:16 aspect ratio, rendered in a soft watercolor painting style. This page features a beautifully integrated design framing the heartfelt message. The background consists of soft, ethereal watercolor washes in shades of warm cream, subtle peach, and hints of muted lavender, creating a gentle, inviting atmosphere. Flowing into this background from the left side are delicate, abstract watercolor elements in soft purples and blues, subtly echoing the nebula from the front cover, as if being painted into existence. The main message text, \"My Dearest Lao Lao, Sometimes I try to imagine my life without you and I honestly can't; it's like trying to imagine a world with no color or laughter. Being with you feels like coming home, and every single day I fall for you a little bit more. You're my absolute everything. All my love, Jordan\", is presented in a beautiful, clean, and slightly stylized white font, centrally placed and easily readable. The typography is elegant and complements the artistic style. The overall composition is visually harmonious, creating an emotional peak for the card with the message as the central focus, surrounded by subtle artistic touches that enhance its sincerity and emotional depth."
